    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors not assessed are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 4. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Relative hemolysis index predictions are within 15% of experimental measurements across all operating points, and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is met. The credibility evidence package supports an Accepted decision.",
